title: Why Doesn’t My Model Work?
blog_posts.content: Machine learning processes are complex, and it's very easy to do things that will cause overfitting without it being obvious. In the worst cases, misleading data can cause the phenomenon known as garbage in garbage out.
author: Michael Lones

title: Where unmarried Americans live
blog_posts.content: Baltimore, the Bronx and Washington, D.C. have the highest rates of unmarried 20-and-older residents among U.S. counties with at least 250,000 such residents overall . Marriage rates are tied to a variety of socioeconomic factors, including income, employment, education and more .
author: Alex Fitzpatrick
